hadiths[56]{hadithnumber,text}:
2436,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi sey ghalla udhaar kharid , aur apni zireh uskey paas rehan rakhi ."
2437,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Madiney main eik Yahudi key paas apni zireh girwi rakh kar us sey apney ghar walon key liye jo hasil kiye .
2438,Hazrat Asma bint Yazeed bin Sakan (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab faut huye to aap ki zireh eik Yahudi key paas ghalley key iwaz girwi rakhi hui thi.
2439,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to aap ki zireh eik Yahudi key paas tees saa jo key badley mein rehan rakhi hui thi .
2440,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawari ka janwer jab rehan rakha jaey to is par sawari ki jaeygi, aur doodh deney wala janwer (gaey, bhens, bakri waghera) jab rehan rakha jaey to uska doodh piya jaeyga. aur janwer ka kharch us shakhs key zimmey hoga jo sawari karta aur doodh peeta hai."
2441,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rehan rakhi hui cheez (mustaqil tor par) qarz khaah key paas nahin rahegi ."
2442,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain jinkey khilaf qiyamat key din mein khud muddai hunga, aur jis key khilaf mein muddai hunga mein us sey muqadma jeet jaunga (lihaza ye teen afraad zarur saza paeyngey.) (eik) wo shakhs jo Allah ka naam ley kar ehad kerey. phir ehad shikni kerey. (doosra) wo jo kisi azad insan ko (ghulam bana kar) bech daley aur uski qeemat kha ley , aur (teesra) wo shakhs jo kisi ko mazdoor rakhey , phir us sey pura kaam ley kar us ko ujrat puri na dey ."
2443,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mazdoor ko uska paseena khushk honey sey pehley mazduri dey do ."
2444,"Hazrat Utba bin Nudr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. aap ney sura Tua-Seen-Meem (Qasas) tilawat farmaai yahan tak key jab Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) key waqiey tak pahunchey ( aayat : 27 , 28 ( to farmaya : Musa ( alehissalam) ney aath das saal pak damani aur pet bhar roti key iwaz mazduri ki."
2445,"Hazrat Hayyan (bin bistaam Hazli (Rahimahullah)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna, unhoney farmaya : mainey yateemi ki haalat mein parwarish pai aur muflisi ki haalat mein hijrat ki. main pet bhar khaney aur (safar key doran mein) apni baari par sawari ki shart par bint ghazawan ka naukar tha. (safar key doran mein) jab wo log (kisi manzil par) thehertey to main unkey liye endhan jama kar key laya karta tha aur jab wo sawar ho kar chaltey to main hudi-khuwani karta (taake oont tez chalen.) Allah ka shukr hai jisney Deen ko sahara (aur taraqqi ka baais) banaya, aur Abu-Hurera ko (deeni aur duniyaawi tor par) Imam (aamil aur governer) bana diya ."
2446,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko faaqa aa gaya . Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko uska ilm huwa to wo kisi kaam ki talash mein nikley taake uskey zariey sey kuch (ujrat) miley jis sey wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khana khilaeyn . wo eik Yahudi key baagh mein ja pahunchey aur uskey liye , eik dol par eik khajoor mazduri ki shart par , satrah dol pani nikala . Yahudi ney aap ko ikhtiyar diya ke satrah ajwa khajuren chun kar ley lein. wo un ( khajuron) ko ley kar Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaey ."
2447,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik khajoor key badley main eik dol pani nikalta tha aur ye shart laga leta tha ke wo umda hogi ."
2448,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ansaar mein sey eik sahab ney aa kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey aap ( key chehra Mubarak) ka rang badla huwa kyon mehsus ho raha hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bhook ( ki wajeh sey) hai. Ansari sahabi apney ghar gaey, ghar mein unhen (khaney ki) koi chiz na mili. wo (kaam ki) talash mein nikal khadey huye . dekha ke eik Yahudi khajoor key darakhton ko pani dey raha tha. Ansari sahabi ney Yahudi sey kaha : kya main tumharey darakhton ko pani dey dun? usney kaha : haan (dey do) aur kaha : har dol ka moawza eik khajoor hogi . Ansari ney shart laga li ke wo kaali, sookhi aur kharab khajoor nahin leingey balke umda khajoor hi leingey. unhoney (baagh ko) pani dey kar uskey iwaz taqriban do saa khajuren hasil kar lin aur unhen ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaey."
2449,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya , aur irshad farmaya : teen tarah key afrad kaasht kar saktey hain : eik wo aadmi jiski zamin hai, wo usey kaasht karta hai, doosra wo jisey kuch zamin ( tohfey key tor par) di gaee , wo us zamin ko kaasht kar sakta hai jo usey di gaee , teesra wo jo soney ya chaandi key iwaz zamin kiraaey par leta hai."
2450,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum mukhaahira par amal kartey they aur is mein harj nahin samajhtey they yahan tak key hamney Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) sey unka ye farman suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai to unki baat sun kar hamney mukhaahira tarak kar diya ."
2451,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum mein sey kuch afrad key paas ( zarurat sey) zayed zameenein thin, wo unhen tihai ya chothai pedawar key iwaz bataai par detey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas zayed zamin ho to wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apney bhai ko kaasht karney dey , agar wo aisey nahin karna chahta to apni zamin apney paas rakhey."
2452,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas zamin hai to wo usey kaasht kerey. ya apney bhai ko kaasht key liye (bila moawza) dey dey , agar wo aisey nahin karna chahta to apni zamin apney paas rakhey."
2453,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat kartey hain ke wo apni zamin key khet kiraaey (thekey) par diya kartey they. unkey paas eik shakhs aaya aur Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees bayan ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kheton ko kiraaey par deney sey mana farmaya hai. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) (Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) key paas) gaey aur main bhi aap key sath gaya . unhoney maqam balaat par un sey mulaqat ki aur ye masla daryaft kya to Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kheton ko kiraaey par deney sey mana farmaya hai, chunanche Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney zamin kiraaey par deni tarak kar di ."
2454,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen khutba diya aur farmaya : jiskey paas zamin ho to wo usey kaasht kerey. ya kisi sey kaasht kara ley, aur usey kiraaey par na dey."
2455,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla sey mana farmaya. aur muhaaqla ka matlab hai zamin kiraaey par dena ."
2456,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney jab logon ko bataai par zamin deney key barey mein bahut baaten kartey suna (ke ye mana hai) to farmaya : subhan Allah ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney to ye farmaya tha : aadmi apney bhai ko zamin kyon nahin dey deta ? aap ney kiraaey par deney sey mana nahin farmaya tha.
2457,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka apney bhai ko (kaasht key liye bila moawza) apni zamin dey dena is baat sey behtar hai ke is par itni itni chiz, yani muqarrar miqdaar wasul kerey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : is mamley ko haql kehtey hain. aur ansaar ki boli mein yehi muhaaqla kahlaata hai."
2458,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Qais (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey masla daryaft kya to unhoney farmaya : hum is shart par zamin kiraaey par detey they ke jo kuch us tukdey mein paida ho, wo tera hai aur jo kuch is tukdey mein paida ho, wo mera hai, to hamen pedawar key iwaz (us andaz sey) zamin kiraaey par deney sey mana kar diya gaya . chaandi ( muqarrar raqam) key iwaz zamin kiraaey par deney sey mana nahin kya gaya ."
2459,"Hazrat abu-Najaashi ( ata bin Suheb Ansari (Rahimahullah)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Raafey bin khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney chacha Hazrat Zuher (bin Raafey bin Adi Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey suna ke unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen eik aisey kaam sey mana farma diya jis mein hamarey liye aasani thi . mainey kaha : jo kuch Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya , wohi durust hai. unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum apney kheton key sath kya kartey ho? hamney kaha : hum unhen (pedawar key) teesrey hissey ya chauthey hissey key iwaz ya gehun aur jo key chand wasq (muqarrara miqdaar) key iwaz kiraaey par dey detey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisey na kya karo, khud kaasht karo ya kisi ko kaasht key liye dey do ."
2460,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum mein sey kisi ko jab apni zamin ki zarurat na hoti to wo usey tihai , chothai ya nisf pedawar key iwaz ( kisi ko kaasht key liye) dey deta aur shart laga leta ke nadi key qarib wali zamin (ki pedawar) mein sey teen chothai, aur gaahi hui gehun ki) gaahey janey sey bach rehney wali) baaliyaan, aur (pani ki chhoti) nali sey sairab honey wali zamin (ki pedawar) uski hogi . us zamaney mein guzraan bahut mushkil thi aur zamin mein lohey ( key aalaat kisi aur phaawdey waghera) sey aur jaisey Allah ko manzoor hota, sey kaam hota tha. wo us sey kuch nafa kama leta tha. phir hamarey paas Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen eik kaam sey mana farma diya hai jis mein (b-zahir) tumhara faeyda tha. ( lekin) Allah ki itaat aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat main tumhara ziyada faeyda hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen muhaaqla sey mana farmatey hain aur irshad farmatey hain : jis ko zamin ki zarurat na ho to wo apney bhai ko Atiya key tor par dey dey , ya rehney dey ."
2461,Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah Taala Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki ghalati maaf farmaaey. qism hai Allah ki ! ye hadees mujhey un sey ziyada malum hai. do aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye jo aapas mein lad padey they. tab aap ney farmaya : agar tum logon ka yehi haal hai to khet bataai par na diya karo . Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney itna jumla sun liya : khet bataai par na diya karo.
2462,"Hazrat Amr bin Dinar (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Taaus (bin kaisaan) (Rahimahullah) sey kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kaash! aap mukhaahira ( bataai par zamin dena) chhod den kyonkey log kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai. unhoney farmaya : aey Amr ! main un ki madad karta hun aur unhen deta hun . aur Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamarey yahan is par amal karaya hai aur unkey badey aalim , yani Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana nahin farmaya lekin ye farmaya tha : koi apney bhai ko (bila moawza zameen) dey dey to ye is par muqarrar moawza leney sey behtar hai."
2463,"Hazrat Taaus (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, ( unhoney farmaya) Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein , Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman Raziallahu anhum key zamana khilaafat mein tihai aur chothai ki shart par zamin kiraaey par di . aur aaj tak usi par amal hota aa raha hai."
2464,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi farmaya tha : agar koi apney bhai ko zamin bila moawza dey dey to ye kaam uskey liye muqarrar karda theka leney sey behtar hai."
2465,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein muhaaqla kartey they. unhoney bayan kya ke phir unkey eik chacha (Hazrat Zuher bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu)) ney aa kar unhen kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka irshad hai : jis key paas zamin ho to wo usey ghalley ki muqarrar miqdaar key iwaz kiraaey par na dey ."
2466,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kuch logon ki zamin mein un ki ijazat key baghair fasal kaasht kar li to usey us fasal mein sey kuch nahin milega , aur uska kharch usey wapis kar diya jaeyga."
2467,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar walon sey phalon aur ghalley ki nisf pedawar key iwaz ( kaashtkaari ka) muahida farmaya.
2468,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key rehney walon ( yahudiyon) ko wahan key khajuron key baghaat aur zamin nisf pedawar key iwaz ( kaam karney key liye) ata farmaai .
2469,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar Fateh kya to usey nisf ( pedawar) key iwaz (kaasht key liye) dey diya ."
2470,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath khajuron key eik baagh mein sey guzra to aap ney dekha ke log khajuron ko pewand laga rahey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye log kya kar rahey hain? mainey kaha : nar darkht ( key gaabhey) sey ley kar mada darkht key ( phoolon key khoshay key) andar rakh rahey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey khayal main to iska koi faeyda nahin . Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko ye irshad malum huwa to ye kaam chhod kar darakhton sey utar aaye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko iski ittilaa hui to farmaya : ye to ( mera) khayal tha. agar us sey faeyda hota hai to kar liya karo. main to tum jaisa insan hi hun aur (insan ka) khayal ghalat bhi ho sakta hai aur sahih bhi ho sakta hai. lekin main jis masley main tumhen yun kahun : Allah ney farmaya to main Allah par kabhi jhoot nahin bolunga ."
2471,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kuch (logon ki) aawazen sunai den to aap ney farmaya : ye aawaz kaisi hai? arz kya gaya : log khajuron ko pewand laga rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : agar wo aisey na karen to bhi durust hai. chunanche Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney us saal pewand na lagaey to phal bahut kharab aaya . unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye soorate-haal arz ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhari duniya ka koi maamla ho to usey khud (apney tajribat aur raey ki roshni mein) anjam dey liya karo. agar tumharey Deen ka maamla ho to meri taraf ruju kya karo.
2472,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman teen chizon mein shareek hain : pani, ghaas aur aag mein . aur un ki qeemat lena haram hai.' (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad) Hazrat abu-Saeed (Abdullah bin Saeed bin Husain) (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : pani sey murad jari pani (darya , nehar , nadi waghera) hai."
2473,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen chizon sey roka na jaey : pani , ghaas aur aag sey ."
2474,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! kon si chiz ko rok rakhna halal nahin? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani, namak aur aag ko. ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : mainey arz kya : ye pani jo hai us ( ki ahmiyat) ko hamney jaan liya. namak aur aag ka kya maamla hai? aap ney farmaya : aey Humera jisney (kisi ko) aag di, usney goya wo sara khana sadqa kya jo us aag sey tayyar huwa. aur jisney namak diya, usney goya wo sab kuch sadqa kar diya jo us namak sey durust huwa. aur jisney kisi musalman ko us jagah pani ka ghoont pilaya jahan pani paya jata hai to usney goya eik ghulam azad kya. aur jisney musalman ko wahan pani ka ghoont pilaya jahan pani nahin paya jata to usney isey zinda kar diya ."
2475,"Hazrat Abyaz bin Hammal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney namak ki kaan talab ki jisey, saddey-Maarib ka namak kaha jata hai to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo unhen ata farma di. uskey baad Hazrat Aqraa bin Habis Tamimi (Raziallahu anhu) ney hazir ho kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! mainey zamana jahiliyat mein namak ka wo zakhira dekha hai, wo aisey ilaqey mein hai jahan (peeney ka) pani nahin paya jata. jo shakhs wahan jata hai (hasbe-zarurat) namak ley leta hai. wo musalsal hasil honey waley pani ki tarah hai, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abyaz bin Hammal (Raziallahu anhu) sey namak ki wo jaagir wapis talab farma li. unhoney kaha : main is shart par wapis karta hun ke aap usey meri taraf sey sadqa qarar den . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo teri taraf sey sadqa hai. wo musalsal hasil honey waley pani ki tarah hai. jo wahan jaeyga, is mein sey ley lega . Hazrat farj bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : wo aaj tak isi tarah hai. jo koi wahan jata hai (hasbe-zarurat namak) ley leta hai. Raavi kehta hai : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab un sey namak ka zakhira wapis liya to uskey badley mein unhen jurf murad key maqam par zamin ka tukda aur khajuron ka baagh ata farmaya."
2476,"Hazrat Iyas bin Abd Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kuch logon ko pani farokht kartey dekha to farmaya : pani na becho , mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pani farokht karney sey mana kartey suna hai."
2477,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( zarurat puri karney key baad) bacha huwa pani farokht karney sey mana farmaya."
2478,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi ko zayed pani sey mana nahin karna chahiye taake uskey zariey sey ghaas rok ley ."
2479,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zayed pani na roka jaey, aur kunwen key pani sey mana na kya jaey."
2480,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key khilaf Harra key nadi naalon key barey mein shikayat pesh ki, wo us sey khajuron key baghaat sairab kartey they. Ansari ney kaha : pani guzar kar (meri zamin mein) aaney dijiye . Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney inkar kya, chunanche wo dono apna muqadma ley kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaey . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( dono key بیانات sun kar) farmaya : Zuber ! (apney baagh ko) pani dey kar apney hamsaaey (key baagh) ki taraf pani chhod diya karo. Ansari ko (us faisley sey) nagawari mehsus hui to usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! (aap ney unkey haq mein faisla diya hai) kyonkey wo aap ki phuphi ka beta hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehra Mubarak ka rang tabdeel (ho kar surkh) ho gaya . phir aap ney farmaya : aey Zuber ! (baagh ko) pani do , phir pani rok rakho yahan tak key wo munderon tak pahunch jaey . Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! merey khayal mein ye aayat usi barey mein nazil hui hai : ( فَلَا وَرَبِّكَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ حَتَّىٰ يُحَكِّمُوكَ فِيمَا شَجَرَ بَيْنَهُمْ ثُمَّ لَا يَجِدُوا۟ فِىٓ أَنفُسِهِمْ حَرَجًا مِّمَّا قَضَيْتَ وَيُسَلِّمُوا۟ تَسْلِيمًا (chunanche aey Nabi !) aap key rab ki qism ! wo eman waley nahin ho saktey jab tak aapas key ikhtilaf mein aap ko haakim na maan lein , phir jo faisley aap un mein kar den , un sey apney dil mein kisi tarah ki tangi aur naakhushi mehsus na keren, aur wo usey dil o jaan sey maan lein."
2481,"Hazrat Solba bin abu-Malik Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wadie-mahzor key Selabi pani key barey mein ye faisla diya ke ooper wala nichey waley sey (pani leney ka) ziyada haq rakhta hai. ooper wala ( khet ko) takhnon tak pani dey , phir apney sey nichey waley ki taraf pani chhod dey ."
2482,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wadi mahzor key Sailabi pani key barey mein ye faisla diya ke aadmi pani rokey yahan tak key takhnon tak pani pahunch jaey, phir wo (doosrey key liye) pani chhod dey ."
2483,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sailab key pani sey khajuron key baagh ko seenchney key barey mein ye faisla diya ke ooper wala nichey waley sey pehley pani ley, aur pani takhnon tak chhoda jaey, phir pani us sey muttasil nichey waley ki taraf chhod diya jaey, isi tarah (silsila jari rahey) yahan tak key baagh khatam ho jaeyn ya pani khatam ho jaey."
2484,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : pani pilaney key din pehley ghodon ko pilaya jaey (oonton aur bakron sey pehley ghodon ko pani pilaya jaey)."
2485,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo taqseem zamanae-jahiliyat mein ho chuki hai, wo jis tarah taqseem ho gaee hai isi tarah rahegi. aur jo taqseem Islam key zamaney mein hogi, wo Islam key tariqa taqseem key mutabiq hogi ."
2486,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kunwaan khoda to chaalis haath zamin uskey maweshiyon key bethney key liye hai."
2487,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kunwen ka Hareem (mutalliqa raqba) uskey rassey ki lambaai key barabar hota hai."
2488,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke agar khajuron key baagh mein eik, do ya teen darkht kisi doosrey shakhs key hon, aur un mein ikhtilaf ho jaey (ke kis ki kitni zamin hai) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla diya ke har darkht ki jad sey ley kar jahan tak uski shaakhen pahunchti hain, wo us darkht ka raqba hai."
2489,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khajoor key darkht ka hareem uski shaakhon key phailaao tak hai."
2490,"Hazrat Saeed bin Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney koi ghar ya zamin ka tukda ( khet ya baagh waghera) farokht kya aur uski qeemat ko us jaisi chiz mein kharch na kya to wo is laaiq hai ke is mein barkat na di jaey.) (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey ye riwayat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah bayan ki hai."
2491,"Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney makaan becha aur uski qeemat ko us jaisi chiz mein kharch na kya to usey is mein barkat hasil nahin hogi."
